&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/media/shared/img/got-my-crac-license/crac_a_lic.png&#34; alt=&#34;A类业余电台操作证书（正面）&#34;  /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/media/shared/img/got-my-crac-license/crac_a_lic_back.png&#34; alt=&#34;A类业余电台操作证书（背面）&#34;  /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
